data.description: Check out this Move in Ready updated home in Horseshoe Gardens subdivision. This 3 bed 2 bath 1806 square feet home has been updated throughout and has a huge backyard complete with a privacy fence. The entire home was completely remodeled in 2016 with porcelain floors and crown molding throughout the home. Also the roof, exterior and interiors doors, light fixtures, recessed lighting, bathroom vanities, toilets, tub/shower, and the AC were updated in 2016 as well. You will love this location and the quiet neighborhood. Schedule a showing today.
